---
<section class="student-report">
  <div class="report-preview" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="report-cover">
      <span class="cover-label">PDF • 13 pages</span>
      <strong>Étude de cas</strong>
      <span>IA chez PragmatIQ (2025)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metrics">
      <div class="metric-card">
        <p>6 mois de déploiements</p>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <p>11 personnes impliquées</p>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <p>8 projets</p>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-card">
        <p>7 succès</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Exemple de déploiement de l’IA : le cabinet PragmatIQ à Poznań</h2>
    <p>Six mois de déploiements : 8 projets, 11 personnes. Bilan de ce qui a fonctionné et de ce que nous avons abandonné.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Cas d’usage par département : finance, comptabilité, administration, marketing, équipes métiers</li>
      <li>Ce qui est passé en production et ce qui est resté en pilote</li>
      <li>Risques et enseignements : données, habitudes, temps, réputation</li>
      <li>Recommandations : base de connaissances, culture de l’expérimentation, suivi du ROI</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a
        href="/Transformation-IA-PragmatIQ-Expertise-et-Performance.pdf"
        class="pdf-download-btn"
        download
        data-event="download_pragmatiq_report"
      >
        <span class="pdf-icon">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </span>
        Télécharger le PDF
        <span class="download-icon">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline>
            <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://pragmatiq.pl/aktualnosci/wydalismy-raport-ai-w-pragmatiq"
        class="cta-secondary"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Perspective client
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .student-report {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-items: center;
    background: #f8f8fa;
  }
  .report-preview {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .report-cover {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(17, 28, 68, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid #e4e9f0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .report-cover strong {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #1a1f36;
  }
  .report-cover span {
    color: #50627a;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cover-label {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: #e6f8f2;
    color: #187650;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .metric-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border: 1px solid #e4e9f0;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(17, 28, 68, 0.06);
  }
  .metric-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #1a1f36;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: #555;
  }
  .content ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 1.2rem;
    color: #3d4b5c;
  }
  .content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }
  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .pdf-download-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b6b48 0%, #187650 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(11, 107, 72, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    width: fit-content;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .pdf-download-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(11, 107, 72, 0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a5a3d 0%, #0b6b48 100%);
  }
  .cta-secondary {
    color: #187650;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 4px;
  }
  .cta-secondary:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .pdf-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .download-icon {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }
  .pdf-download-btn:hover .download-icon {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .student-report {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .report-preview {
      align-items: center;
    }
    .report-cover {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cover-label {
      align-self: center;
    }
    .content ul {
      text-align: left;
    }
    .cta-group {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
